{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2bda03551d","title":"党组织赐给党员六件法宝","origin":"《重庆市右派言论选辑第二集》（内部文件，只供领导同志参考，请勿外传和翻印），中共重庆市委宣传部办公室编印，1957年8月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3b23471da0","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"2bda03551d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"3d6e05a0be","name":"重庆"},{"id":"46c21f5fce","name":"陈民锋"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"43f88c5ff0","type":"title","text":"党组织赐给党员六件法宝","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bda03551d"},{"id":"cdee28e3e9","type":"authors","text":"重庆陈民锋","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bda03551d"},{"id":"0e387fc70f","type":"paragraph","text":"[编者按：陈民锋，旧职员成分。现在重庆市百货公司工作。这篇文章是对共产党员、共青团员、积极分子进行恶毒的污蔑丑化。]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bda03551d"},{"id":"292553efc7","type":"paragraph","text":"党员不是真正特殊材料制成的，党赐给党员六件法宝：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bda03551d"},{"id":"9ef144cca2","type":"paragraph","text":"1．合金饭碗：在高温热下，不会熔化。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bda03551d"},{"id":"40ebabb987","type":"paragraph","text":"2．直升飞机：青云直上，步步登天。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bda03551d"},{"id":"c5a7ff5156","type":"paragraph","text":"3．戒尺一把：高高在上，好为人师，你说得不对，给你一戒尺。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bda03551d"},{"id":"53edabed9c","type":"paragraph","text":"4．朝笏：直接面见君王的权利，","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bda03551d"},{"id":"fabc83288c","type":"appellation","text":"5．免死金牌：犯了错误、不受处分。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bda03551d"},{"id":"9ed875e560","type":"paragraph","text":"6．上方宝剑：先斩后奏。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bda03551d"},{"id":"b50e6e354a","type":"paragraph","text":"另外，赐给有党员阴阳枪、绣花鞋、录音机。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bda03551d"},{"id":"d45d694201","type":"paragraph","text":"团员起了脱离群众的助手作用。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bda03551d"},{"id":"a8bbef078c","type":"paragraph","text":"1．在运动中，党员是发号司令，团员是摇旗呐喊。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bda03551d"},{"id":"1e1a905b57","type":"paragraph","text":"2．工资福利，先党员后团员。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bda03551d"},{"id":"0f2cf888d6","type":"paragraph","text":"积极分子特别突出，一看就会扬威耀武，有人说他们是腬电报，录音机、传话筒、积极分子是糟极分子，入党糟极，提拔整人糟极，积极只是批评别人积极，开会端板凳积极，工资福利积极。（本文题目是原编者所加）","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bda03551d"}],"page":{"id":"0845d05b6c","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bda03551d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}